  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-align:justify;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: -9px 0px;padding: 0px 9px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 15px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;border-left: 1px solid rgb(192, 200, 209);border-right: 1px solid rgb(192, 200, 209);visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: center;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;visibility: visible;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“我们正在做的事情，就是以工具作为切入点，去聚合更多创作者和爱好者，帮助他们成长为下一代的宫崎骏、鸟山明、诺兰们。”刘耕说。</span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2026年1月11日，一款中国AI短剧产品，登顶了Product Hunt日榜。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: center;line-height: 0;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 676.997px;visibility: visible;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5703703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;width: 676.997px !important;visibility: visible !important;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a6f5d735&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FqSup0XIHCCicSVWBPTKeI1ApicVdKficibEu8Tib0EhW3vHribyXEfYfAO3s5GPic1vRwwTmBZQ5QWvrMNstuK8BnOCibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D0\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">作为一款获评界面新闻2025年Real100创新家的AI应用产品，Elser.AI自2025年12月15日正式上线以来，在国内外市场迅速突破，短短20余天，就得到资深AI产品体验官的推荐，并冲到Product Hunt日榜榜一。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: center;line-height: 0;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 676.997px;visibility: visible;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1787037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;width: 676.997px !important;visibility: visible !important;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8176d6c0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FqSup0XIHCCicSVWBPTKeI1ApicVdKficibEu5ib8hia0Sa6OVFzOL3XxxpgtbtAHEpzCVxSXnzjH0uWcRBhNVDs6g5Hw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">用户对Elser.AI的评价，集中在“高度一致性”，“精细分镜控制”，“一站式成片”这几个关键词上。这几个AI短剧或影视行业的长期痛点正在被Elser.AI解决。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在这样的背景下，我们访谈了Elser.AI的创始人刘耕，他分享了Elser.AI对于AI短剧乃至整个AI视频行业的理解。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:19px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">更专业的同时，也要“更接地气”</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2025年是大视频模型高速发展的一年，制作一个AI视频已经并不困难。但“成片”不等于作品，如何持续提升AI创作的天花板，让AI不是电子垃圾的催化剂，而是优质作品的加速器，依然是大模型应用产品和创业者需要一起努力的方向。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">据刘耕介绍，更好地帮助“人机协作”，让更多优质“作品”涌现，是Elser.AI长期关注的方向。Elser.AI致力于成为“高手可控、新手简单”的Agent工具。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在剧本处理上，Elser提供了面向Pro的“剧本还原”模式，和面向爱好者的“一键成文”模式。在分镜生成上，Elser在Basic Mode外，将在近期推出更专业、更精细化的Studio Mode。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: center;line-height: 0;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5555555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100007223\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=94060639&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F9CRQL8peAG0c5EOHTt9vYU4Kkenb08gdk6HicmRpy5Z35iafhjpHCvnzVia8TGOJVrLbTBsXXYXWcpXETKyaF8Xiaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">漫剧的生成主要有“图生视频”和“参考生视频”两个主流路径，分别被戏称为“多参宗”和“首尾宗”。在Elser.AI的Studio Mode中则实现了两宗归一。专业用户可以选择自己熟悉的路径，调用几乎市面上所有成熟的模型，对分镜图片和视频进行精细化的调控。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在短剧Agent外，Elser.AI还开放了两个真正“0操作”一键到底的Agent功能，分别是AI广告和IP SHOW。只需要上传一张产品图、一张IP角色图，AI就能自动解析图片内容，在3分钟内帮你生成一段酷炫的产品宣传视频，或IP的角色秀场。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(248, 15, 20);\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">上线一个月至今，Elser.AI持续迭代，从短剧Agent快速向整合多模型多工具的创作者社区衍生。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">当被问及这样的迭代是否会影响Elser.AI\"挑剔级”短剧Agent的品牌心智时，刘耕回答：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“AI漫剧和短剧很热，但要打造一部爆款短剧，仍需要创作者在剧本、编导、镜头语言、剪辑后期上具备审美和专业知识。当下，AI短剧和漫剧还不是爱好者入局就能快速变现的生意；仍然更适合有一定基础的短剧公司或工作室。但从长远来看，AI给了每个人创作平权的机会。当下，AI视频工具在全球视频工具中的市场份额占比仍然低于1%，在专业视频创作者中的渗透率也不到10%。这个赛道仍有几十倍的增长空间。”</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:19px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: left;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">AI视频工具的竞争优势是什么&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">据不完全统计，2025年市面上仅AI短剧工具就有三四十种。当问到刘耕，面对如此激烈的竞争，Elser.AI如何持续保持产品的优势时，他分享了四点看法：</span></p>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: right;justify-content: flex-end;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\">\n    <div style=\"align-self:center;padding:20px;margin:0px;display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:100%;flex:100 100 0%;width:auto;height:auto;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: justify;\">\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(248, 15, 20);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">1、真正的先发优势是什么？</span></strong></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">率先跑出来的工具，在用户操作习惯和用户资产沉淀上，会形成自己的壁垒。但这层壁垒比不上“创作者社区”形成的关系链和变现路径。从工具成长为创作者社区后，会形成各种分享协作、变现的关系链：有专业创作者为爱好者提供模板、制作教程、获取收益；有编剧在社区中寻找编导；有组织把产线搬到平台上，完成管理和交付……而创作者社区的壁垒，又不及消费型社区。跑通了消费型社区，将对创作者社区产生虹吸效应。世界上90%以上的人只需要享受创作者内容给他们提供的满足，但这90%以上的消费型用户贡献了平台核心的流量、时长和变现空间。</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: right;justify-content: flex-end;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\">\n    <div style=\"align-self:center;padding:20px;margin:0px;display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:100%;flex:100 100 0%;width:auto;height:auto;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: justify;\">\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(248, 15, 20);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2、当下AI视频工具市场格局未定。</span></strong></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在当下，任何一个AI视频工具都很难说已有“头部优势”。因为AI视频工具的形态远没有定型，依然有巨大的创新空间。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">比如在创作中，仅通过对话框操控修改图片、视频的问题在于：</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">（1）</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(255, 99, 103);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">表达问题</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">。</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">大多数人其实无法非常清晰地表达自己的意图，再经过大模型处理后，更容易出现预期错位。大模型并没有读心能力，有歧义的语言会带来偏离需求的结果。但如果创作者不明白背后的机制，往往会归咎于模型和工具。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">（2）</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(255, 99, 103);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">效率问题</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">。</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果让AI辅助剪辑视频，它要先理解创作者的意图，这中间本身就存在“牛头不对马嘴”的问题。比如创作者觉得视频节奏慢，大模型选择对视频进行加速；但其实这个节奏慢是因为有过多的冗余镜头需要裁掉。而人可能只需要扫一眼或剪一刀就能解决。一旦需要稳定交付，效率和质量才是关键要素。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">（3）</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(255, 99, 103);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">审美问题</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">。AI在审美上依然和创作者存在长期的隔膜。大模型追求的是“平均”上的好，但创作者的趣味千差万别。而图形化操作的好处就在于，当沟通不成立时，创作者可以直接上手。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">长期来看，视频工具一定是多种交互方式的融合。对话、画布/分镜板、剪辑板，当下仍是文字、图片、影像最高效的交互形态。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">而Elser.AI下一步努力的方向，是融合现有的交互形态，贴合用户的个性化诉求，为他们规划/选择更符合他们习惯的操作和调度方式。今年计划推出的产品形态，也会更具想象空间。</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: right;justify-content: flex-end;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\">\n    <div style=\"align-self:center;padding:20px;margin:0px;display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:100%;flex:100 100 0%;width:auto;height:auto;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: justify;\">\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(248, 15, 20);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">3、差异化的定位和场景。</span></span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">视频的场景足够丰富。单以动画为例，漫剧和社媒营销场景的ACG内容场景差异很大。社媒内容追求的是快速响应热点，快速完成交付。Elser.AI曾花几分钟做了1个30秒的短片，在抖音跑了2000多万的播放量，一条视频涨粉破万。但漫剧对叙事逻辑、故事冲突、角色塑造、镜头语言是有更高要求的。稳定高效的可交付能力成为了工具的首要能力。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">当被问道“作为字节跳动出来，并熟知社媒运营逻辑的创业者，为什么不先聚焦于社媒内容，而是选择了交付标准更高的AI短剧和漫剧内容”时，刘耕回答，因为社媒内容有现成更好的分发平台，从工具到平台的路径是非常艰难、不明朗的，就像Sora2的内容都流向了Tiktok。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">但漫剧和游戏，可能存在平台级机会。现有的社媒并未提供一个沉浸式的幻想世界，而幻想的维度是无限的。存在的荒芜和孤寂感，可能是这个时代很多人的痛点。这也是“死了么”这种APP能够迅速蹿红的底层原因。我们以漫剧为入口，也会拓展更多的AI互动和娱乐形态。</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: right;justify-content: flex-end;display: flex;flex-flow: row;\">\n    <div style=\"align-self:center;padding:20px;margin:0px;display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:100%;flex:100 100 0%;width:auto;height:auto;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: justify;\">\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(248, 15, 20);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">4、拼“内容”+拼“效率”。</span></strong></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">当下，已经产出“爆款内容”的工具，也有先发优势。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">很多漫剧工具在宣传中，都会提到哪些爆款漫剧使用了自己的产品。可以说，爆款内容，天然为工具提供了品牌和流量的优势。Elser.AI自己也有多部剧集和头部平台达成合作，即将上线。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">不过刘耕坦言：内容是否能做爆，工具并不占决定性因素。决定内容爆发的，还是团队自身的人才密度，对漫剧这种内容形态的理解。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">工作流的架构和智能化差异，反馈在提示词产出质量、图片/视频产出速度和抽卡率的巨大差异上。Elser.AI对自己内容团队的要求是，使用市面上一切工具进行横向对比，如果Elser.AI无法实现效率和成本的领先，内容团队可以使用其他工具。不过经过多番对比后，他们发现Elser.AI的产出效率和稳定性都有3倍以上的提升。</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 19px;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">优质内容是毕生所求</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">刘耕很喜欢《牧羊少年奇幻之旅》里的一句话：“当你真心渴望某样东西时，整个宇宙都会联合起来帮助你完成。”&nbsp;</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“而帮助更多人创造好的内容，这件事可能就是我内心渴望的‘天命’。”刘耕说。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">从12岁开始发表小说，作为理科生，刘耕因为热爱写作，上北大选择了文科专业。十余年美学研究生涯，研究了绘画、小说、电影等多种艺术形态，熟知各个时代、各个民族的表达方式。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">但他发现，研究并不是他最开始想做的事情。他更喜欢的是创造，以及能和一群热爱内容创作者一起创造。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">因此刘耕离开学界，尝试做过IP音频产品，在字节做过语文、美术等教育产品，帮助过许多抖音创作者成长，一直都是在围绕“优质内容”做事情。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“我们正在做的事情，就是以工具作为切入点，去聚合更多创作者和爱好者，帮助他们成长为下一代的宫崎骏、鸟山明、诺兰们。”刘耕说，AI漫剧和短剧是一个超过千亿级的市场，当下最大的痛点不是工具，而是优质内容的稀缺。因此，Elser.AI团队也即将推出自己的创作者培训计划，以及面向国内创作者的小说Agent。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5111111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100007220\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7f7456ac&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F9CRQL8peAG0c5EOHTt9vYU4Kkenb08gducVtUqsBWXmoKeuVuVPbuz1rDEE0mD1qmZsz1Ox5icz1Fbia6m0VTZ6w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5074074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100007221\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=55b273cc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F9CRQL8peAG0c5EOHTt9vYU4Kkenb08gd87tOCUTvvYnDibvrPb9xAMS30gOlIrSoXjKdEfiblenom0pR9mKicXr0g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">优质的内容永远处于相对的稀缺状态。这件事情认真做，上限可以像迪士尼一样从工作室成长为厂牌，成长为IP宇宙。但当下，优质的AI原生内容平台，依然可以说是空白，机会是非常明确的。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">而创作与表达，是宇宙赐予人类的“无限次”重生机会。AI，则把这一权利，交付给所有人。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文通过访谈 Elser.AI 创始人刘耕，探讨了 AI 短剧工具如何通过提升一致性与效率，从单一工具演进为创作者社区及内容生态。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文通过访谈 Elser.AI 创始人刘耕，探讨了 AI 短剧工具如何通过提升一致性与效率，从单一工具演进为创作者社区及内容生态。",
  "summary": "文章围绕登顶 Product Hunt 日榜的 AI 短剧产品 Elser.AI，展开了对创始人刘耕的深度访谈。核心内容涵盖了 AI 视频行业的痛点解决、竞争壁垒构建以及未来生态演进。刘耕指出，Elser.AI 通过解决“高度一致性”和“精细分镜控制”等技术难题，实现了从“成片”到“作品”的跨越。文章详细讨论了 AI 视频工具的四种竞争优势：从工具向创作者及消费型社区的转化、交互形态的融合创新、差异化场景的深耕，以及内容与效率的并行。创始人强调，AI 的终极价值在于实现创作平权，而 Elser.AI 的目标是构建一个聚合创作者、具备沉浸式体验的 AI 原生内容生态。 ",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 视频工具的竞争核心将从单一工具属性转向创作者社区及消费型社区。",
      "explanation": "工具形成的壁垒有限，通过社区建立的关系链、变现路径以及消费型用户带来的流量虹吸效应，才是长期的核心竞争力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "视频工具的交互形态将走向对话、画布、分镜板与剪辑板的多维融合。",
      "explanation": "单纯的对话框操控存在表达歧义、效率低下和审美隔膜等问题，图形化与自动化结合的交互更符合专业交付需求。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 漫剧和短剧市场潜力巨大，但目前最大的瓶颈在于优质内容的稀缺而非工具本身。",
      "explanation": "虽然 AI 降低了门槛，但爆款仍需深厚的审美与专业知识，工具需在效率和稳定性上实现数倍提升才能支撑专业交付。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 视频工具在专业创作者中的渗透率仍低，存在几十倍的增长空间。",
      "explanation": "目前 AI 视频占全球视频工具份额不足 1%，随着创作平权的推进，AI 将成为每个人表达与创造的核心驱动力。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "我们正在做的事情，就是以工具作为切入点，去聚合更多创作者和爱好者，帮助他们成长为下一代的宫崎骏、鸟山明、诺兰们。",
    "AI 视频工具的形态远没有定型，依然有巨大的创新空间。",
    "内容是否能做爆，工具并不占决定性因素。决定内容爆发的，还是团队自身的人才密度，对漫剧这种内容形态的理解。",
    "创作与表达，是宇宙赐予人类的'无限次'重生机会。AI，则把这一权利，交付给所有人。"
  ],
